ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Change of the boundary of the Grand Falls District Chamber of Commerce
PrecisOrder approving the application by the GRAND FALLS DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in New Brunswick, to change the boundaries of its district from the Town of Grand Falls, the Parish of Grand Falls, the Parish of Saint-André, the Parish of Drummond and the Parish of Denmark to the Town of Grand Falls, the Parish of Grand Falls, the Parish of Saint-André, the Parish of Drummond, the Parish of Denmark, the LSD of Saint-Léonard, the LSD of Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes, the Village of Sainte-Anne-de-Madawaska and the LSD of Sainte-Anne-de-Madawaska.
AttachmentsAttachment
precis: Order approving the application by the GRAND FALLS DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in New Brunswick, to change the boundaries of its district from the Town of Grand Falls, the Parish of Grand Falls, the Parish of Saint-André, the Parish of Drummond and the Parish of Denmark to the Town of Grand Falls, the Parish of Grand Falls, the Parish of Saint-André, the Parish of Drummond, the Parish of Denmark, the LSD of Saint-Léonard, the LSD of Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes, the Village of Sainte-Anne-de-Madawaska and the LSD of Sainte-Anne-de-Madawaska.
